### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Model info
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/model-info

### Coverage
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/coverage

### Predict by coordinates (longitude + latitude)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickup_longitude": -73.9855,
  "pickup_latitude": 40.7580,
  "dropoff_longitude": -73.7781,
  "dropoff_latitude": 40.6413,
  "pickup_datetime": "2016-06-12 08:30:00"
}

### Predict by coordinates without pickup_datetime
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickup_longitude": -73.9855,
  "pickup_latitude": 40.7580,
  "dropoff_longitude": -73.7781,
  "dropoff_latitude": 40.6413
}

### Predict by address (city/place names)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict-by-address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickup_address": "Times Square, New York",
  "dropoff_address": "JFK Airport, Queens, NY",
